\lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid6966664\charrsid3227017 Women\rquote s}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid15302494\charrsid3227017  Guild you call it here, but we call it the Mothers Meeting at the church.
