\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid6893039 ML  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid15302494\charrsid3227017 Oh well, if there was any little job in the house, he never went o
ut through the week. It was at the weekends when they used to go out, up to the market the two did. On a Saturday night like and that. But - he never went out much through the week. Because - there always was some little job - maybes someone's running dow
n, shoes mending and that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid10622400 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid15302494\charrsid3227017 Who did your mother go out with when she went to the Mothers Meeting?
