Well I - I think she really went with the neighbour next door. Mrs Boyle they called her. And I think she went really - with her.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid10622400 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid15302494\charrsid3227017 Did your mother go anywhere else to enjoy herself that you remember?
