as in all week, there was only the weekend when he used to when him and mother used to go out.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid10622400 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid15302494\charrsid3227017 Did your father attend any clubs or pubs?
