\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid6893039 ML  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid15302494\charrsid3227017 No, she was only - she was a Co-o
p woman. Aye, she always dealt with the to-op she did. She - if she had anything it used to be in the Co-op where she used to put in.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid10622400 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid15302494\charrsid3227017 Was this any special boot club, sick club or funeral club or anything?

