Well - maybe she'd go to their house and see them and have a - a matter and then she'd - maybe they would come into our house and have a matter with her.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid10622400 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid15302494\charrsid3227017 Would these be neighbours or friends from across the town?
