place}}Darlington{\*\xmlclose}, 'cos when - me father was father died, he left him some - houses. Well then after he died well they had to be sold and come to us. An
d 'course - I had to go - we had to go down - to see the solicitor about them. And that was the only time when I come in contact with any of them.
