 o'clock at night. My father used to go to work at four o'clock in the morning and it was six o'clock man a time when he got home at night.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid10622400 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid15302494\charrsid3227017 Where did you say he worked, he was a boilerman wasn't he?
