Oh well - they used to visit us all did the clergy you - them days they used to visit you every week. Oh yes. They visit you every week they did. And if anyone was ill, well they used to visit them every day.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid10622400 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid15302494\charrsid3227017 Did you ever go to confession?
