Well we generally used to go for the weekend you see, 'cos you go to Communion on the Sunday, maybe we'd go on a }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid6966664\charrsid3227017 Friday}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid15302494\charrsid3227017  or on a Saturday.
