He - used to take him out like when I wasn't with him. But - if we went out, we generally used to take him away out in the country up by Staindrop there before they altered it and - round by Monk End and there, we used to take him all over.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid10622400 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid15302494\charrsid3227017 Walking?
